{"tid":542432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(蛔vs共) 傳12萬新疆維人 送再教育營","createTime":"2018-01-27T12:52:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-27T14:38:32.000Z","uid":53705,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3d0bacf0feac1306876fd8a099bdb7668771601b","tid":542432,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T12:52:51.000Z","msg":"海外傳媒估算，新疆約有十二萬維族回教徒目前被投送「再教育營」。據報，喀什市共四個營地，其中一個在喀什郊外的「再教育營」，是幢新建、類似監獄的白色建築，設有看守塔，圍牆上布滿鐵絲網。有曾被拘押人士指，原供八人居住的房間關了十四人，人們不能平躺，在寒冷天氣仍要赤腳。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20180127/mobile/odn-20180127-0127_00178_012.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20180127%2Fmobile%2Fodn-20180127-0127_00178_012.html&d=UMA%2FSFSLGIuJQGbdLu604TOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=1ce25268\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20180127/mobile/odn-20180127-0127_00178_012.html</a><br />\n<br />\n中共vs蛔<br />\n兩大毒瘤對決, 連登仔支持邊個??"},{"pid":"2d91b1d2af0a1940bffd2284cd0a06442b2d6400","tid":542432,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T12:55:39.000Z","msg":"新集中(教育)營<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70133faba8555443f79b6b8f9731f974acb9c374","tid":542432,"uid":89931,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T12:57:20.000Z","msg":"凡是敵人反對的，我們就要擁護；凡是敵人擁護的，我們就要反對。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6fd9b48edce7ff443d13c0c78c0b31f3b8161d5","tid":542432,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"70133faba8555443f79b6b8f9731f974acb9c374","tid":542432,"uid":89931,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T12:57:20.000Z","msg":"凡是敵人反對的，我們就要擁護；凡是敵人擁護的，我們就要反對。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T12:57:48.000Z","msg":"但中共和蛔 都是敵人, 咁點搞??"},{"pid":"b8511cde44390f928c41478aee9d24a24f4f256d","